node.text: We all have our own goals and ambitions, should this be affirming our freedom, expressing our femininity, or finding our inner power. And we shouldn’t let anyone prevent us from doing so. This is why #WeWearRouge , to give us the confidence and power to achieve our goals. We wear Rouge as a statement, a symbol of our unapologetic femininity. Even while being at home most of the time , I just love the feeling of putting on a red lip in the morning and instantly feeling like you can conquer the day. I wear Rouge not for anyone outside, just for me! And on the days where I feel less motivated, I just need a touch of that perfect transfer-proof red to feel good again. Wearing Rouge means so much more than just a mark of lipstick, it’s the mark I want to leave on the world! #RougeDior @diormakeup
